liblightstone
------------------------------------------
This is a C-based development library for the Lightstone, a Biometric USB
device distributed with the Journey to Wild Divine Relaxation Software
(https://wilddivine.com/)

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.7-1
  liblightstone-devel-1.5+git20120116-1bl2
  liblightstone1.5.0-1.5+git20120116-1bl2
  libusb1.0-1.0.21-1
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.44-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  libusb1.0-devel-1.0.21-1
  ninja-1.12.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/qdot/liblightstone

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/qdot/liblightstone.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack liblightstone-1.5+git20120116-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./liblightstone-1.5+git20120116-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/liblightstone-1.5+git20120116-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liblightstone-1.5+git20120116-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liblightstone1.5.0-1.5+git20120116-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liblightstone-devel-1.5+git20120116-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(liblightstone)
  /usr/bin/lightstone_test.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/liblightstone.README
  /usr/share/doc/liblightstone/AUTHORS.txt
  /usr/share/doc/liblightstone/ChangeLog.txt
  /usr/share/doc/liblightstone/LICENSE.txt
  /usr/share/doc/liblightstone/README.asciidoc

(liblightstone1.5.0)
  /usr/bin/cyglightstone-1.5.0.dll

(liblightstone-devel)
  /usr/include/lightstone/lightstone.h
  /usr/lib/liblightstone.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/liblightstone.pc

------------------

